
 - When 'preview' option is selected, raytracing could be done at a smaller
   resolution. Then you could select an area of this image to be rendered at
   real resolution.

 - Preview could also be done using ZBuffer renderer. Selecting an area could
   make this to be raytraced.

 - Add the possibility to "merge" another scene into the current one.

 - In the image window, we should be able to apply any image filter to a
   selected area.
